Maximised by default, with various grids already in place for content to show up later

Steps for 1 complete cycle of omr
1) Add/open project
2) select template file
3) select regions while inputting data about those regions
4) select output folder
5) generate template
6) select input folder
7) process

Preliminary:
Errors always return to select regions interface (with regions already selected)
user to go back even further if necessary

Expected Final:
Errors return to appropriate step after determining cause of error